	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Recte vero cogitas, quales hic habeamus homines in republica, atque utinam non potentiores pene omnes ita essent affecti!</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pauci supersunt in senatu (ex inferioribus tamen), qui libertatem salvam retinere velint.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pessimum est, quod religio et salus fidelium eorumque petitiones ubique praetexuntur.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ea specie seducuntur simpliciores ex civibus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miror vero illos tam patienter nostras contradictiones ferre posse; ringuntur quidem mirum in modum, interea dissimulant; nam saepe expectavi, ut vocaremur ad senatum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed fortassis conclusionem expectant, ut postea communi authoritate nos premant.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus frangat ipsorum consilia.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Potes cogitare, quę sit sors nostra nunc hic docentium et pastorum partes agentium.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus confirmet et custodiat suos!</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interea vero nihil amplius in isto negotio actum est.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego pro infoelici et infausto omine habeo, quod nuncius, qui cum literis nuper <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l301" cert="high">Lugdunum</placeName> ad <placeName type="auto_name">Lemovicensem</placeName> missus est, in itinere, antequam ad ipsum perveniret, periit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam sic universa illa machinatio pereat!</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ita mihi faustum esset omen.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alias nihil novi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Sumus valde solliciti</foreign> der handlung halb mitt dem herren von Sax.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott schicke es zum besten; dann es möcht wol ein bösen handel gen.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wil gern hören, was von <placeName ref="l21" cert="high">Baden</placeName> kömm.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas <persName type="citizen_name">Fabritii</persName> remitto et magnas pro hic gratias ago.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aliunde iam nihil habeo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wir hend die <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genffer</placeName> aber einist gar erzürnt, das wir in das foedus nitt consentierend; si hend uns für grob esel, die wir nun unser und nitt der gmeinen kilchen rechnung tragend.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Aber mich dunckt, si wellind uns gern als esel mißbruchen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculi</persName> exemplar ita, ut est, imprimitur;</foreign> so vil hatts gholffen, das man si inen worden; sonst hettend si gar herrliche locos drus zwacket und anders an dstatt gsetzt.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Si dörffends nun nitt ußlon, so si send, das mans innen worden.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid praetermittere voluerint, videbis, cum exemplaria fuerint absoluta.</s>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil aliud nunc habeo, nisi quod dominum oro, ut te diutissime ecclesiae suae servet incolumem.</s>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te d. <persName ref="p8063" cert="high">Steigerus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3494">Diesbachius</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4060">Zähenderi</persName>, socer, fratres item ac symmystae, praesertim <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8416" cert="high">Musculus</persName>, mater item, item et uxor.</s>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta nostro nomine tuos omnes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> 10. martii 1565.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="30" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[ohannes] Hallerus</persName>, semper tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="31" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae pastori fidelissimo, domino et compatri mihi summa semper observantia colendo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
